Package se.idsec.signservice.security.sign.impl

Implementations of signature supporting classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSignerResult<T>
    Abstract base class for SignerResult implementations.
    DefaultSignatureValidationResult
    Default implementation of the SignatureValidationResult interface.
    DefaultSigningCredential Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
    Use BasicCredential instead.
    KeyStoreSigningCredential Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
    Use KeyStoreCredential instead.
    StaticCredentials
    Utility class that holds pre-generated key pairs.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InternalSignatureValidationException
    Exception that may be used internally by implementations of the SignatureValidator interface.
